HEADWORD: Hydrotheca
<hw>Hy`dro*the"ca</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> L. <plw>Hydrothec⟦ae⟧</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>, E.
<plw>Hydrothecas</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL., fr. E.
<ets>hydra</ets> + Gr. <?/ a box.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of
